{"type": "article", "id": 11267, "title": "耐克 Air Tech Challenge Volt 配色", "description": "", "date": "2015-06-26T12:00:12Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 1329, "comment_count": 2, "praise_count": 44, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160606135123qSulTLW5CsQdircD.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t耐克出了那么多鞋款，不管是哪个系列，简约的白色款一直都很畅销。但把白球鞋怎么玩出新意可不简单。今年夏天，耐克推出了 Volt 配色运用于耐克的经典鞋款 Air Tech Challenge 的鞋身上，主色调仍旧是白色，鞋身是皮革与网眼材质的混搭，气垫中底则是带有泼墨细节的白色，鞋舌与后跟部分用荧光黄加以点缀，还配上了一个湖绿色的外底。定价 120 欧元（约合人民币 834 元），<a href=\"https://www.overkillshop.com/de/nike-air-tech-challenge-iii-749957-101.html\" target=\"_blank\">点击这里尝试购买</a>。\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t</p>\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160606135121AyQ7j4LE6G5MUcvY.jpg\" title=\"1\" alt=\"1\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/201606061351224UmElzd3NswbyhO9.jpg\" title=\"1\" alt=\"1\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160606135122LUFVPhvlmQ4ograD.jpg\" title=\"1\" alt=\"1\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n\t</p>\r\n\r\n<div>\r\n\t<br>\r\n</div>\n\n\n"}